    "text": "This family..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.101,
    "endTime": 23.093,
    "text": "But nothing lasts forever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.383,
    "endTime": 29.947,
    "text": "I heard you had to leave in a hurry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.407,
    "endTime": 32.198,
    "text": "It's never easy these days."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.82,
    "endTime": 36.662,
    "text": "So, what are you going to do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.844,
    "endTime": 38.335,
    "text": "I've lived a lot of lives."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.445,
    "endTime": 40.6,
    "text": "But I'm done running from my past."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.898,
